wp.me\/p95VHY-Yf","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":18951,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/01\/shaban-a-month-people-neglect\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sha\u2019ban: Month people neglect between Rajab and Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I do not see you fasting any month as much as you fast during Sha\u2019ban.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is a month people neglect between Rajab and Ramadan. It is a month in which\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/21\/supplication-fasting-never-turned-away\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: Supplication at breaking fast is never rejected","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the supplication of a fasting person is not turned away at the time of breaking fast .\u201d Abdullah would say when breaking fast, \u201cO Allah, I ask You by You mercy, which encompasses all\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s supplication in Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he finished his Witr prayer with invocations of peace, he would say, \u201cGlory to the King, the Holy.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1430 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/07\/water-to-cool-off-while-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Using water to cool off while fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: I have seen the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, in al-\u2018Araj pouring water over his head while he was fasting, either due to thirst or heat. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2365 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0628\u0643\u0631 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25379,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/02\/dua-of-distressed\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication of the distressed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplication of the distressed is this: O Allah, I hope in Your mercy. Do not abandon me to myself, not even for a moment, and take care of all my affairs. There is no God\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14907,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/finish-suhur-adhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":3735,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Finish meal when you hear Fajr call to prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you hears the call to prayer while eating the pre-fasting meal and his vessel is in his hand, let him not put it down until he fulfills his needs from it.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-jso